task.summary:
Add file parser for collecting and storing of data.
Can specify the amount of data to parse (in the form of percentage.)
Also add enum Type, Data object.

Add final ints for data amounts, addLabel method, scanImages Refactor
The code that constructed the relative file path (in scanImages()) for the corresponding data file being used was separated into it's own method, getFilePath(). The same was done for the logic identifying the number of data points in the file: getDataSize().
You can specify how many data points are being used with the final static int variables at the start of the Machine Learning class.
